---

<BaseLayout description={siteConfig.description}>
  <article class="prose lg:prose-xl">
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
      Greetings! My name is
      <b class="text-white-600">Hidayat Taufiqur</b>
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-md">
      <TypedText
        client:load
        messages={funFacts}
        type-speed={55}
        delete-speed={28}
        pause-time={1500}
        between-pause={2000}
        aria-label="Fun facts about me"
      />
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
      I'm a <b>Software Engineer</b> with <b>2+ years</b> of experience, currently
      focused on <b>Dynamics 365 Finance &amp; Operations (D365FO)</b>. I
      specialize in <b>backend engineering</b> and system design.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
      I build APIs, integrate services, and automate workflows (including
      <b>n8n</b>) to make systems reliable and maintainable.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
      Areas I care about: <b>backend architecture</b>, <b>distributed systems</b>,
      and <b>DevOps practices</b> that keep services fast and observable.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Toolbox</h3>
      <ul class="mt-2">
        <li><b>Languages:</b> Java/OpenJDK, JavaScript/TypeScript, Go, Python, C/C++, X++, PHP, Nix</li>
        <li><b>Databases:</b> PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Redis, Firebase, Microsoft SQL Server</li>
        <li><b>Platforms:</b> Linux, GCP, Nix/NixOS</li>
        <li><b>Frameworks:</b> Node.js, Laravel, Flask, D365FO/X++</li>
        <li><b>Web/Infra:</b> Nginx, Docker, REST APIs, integrations</li>
        <li><b>Automation:</b> n8n, basic CI/CD</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
      Outside work, I enjoy movies, music, guitar, and the occasional game
      session. I also like tinkering with my dev environment.
    </p>

    <p class="text-lg mt-8">
      Interested in learning more about my professional background? Please check
      my <b>
        <a
          href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XiM2WTfmVllMGRBhwis-Bgl9DPlVrKcC/view?usp=sharing"
          target="_blank"
          aria-label="View my CV/resume">CV/resume!</a
        >
      </b>
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 p-3 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
      <p class="text-sm">
        ðŸ’¼ While I'm currently focused on ERP development, I'm actively seeking
        opportunities in backend engineering and system architecture roles.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <p class="text-lg">Let's connect:</p>
      <div class="flex gap-x-4 gap-y-2 flex-wrap mt-4">
        {
          siteConfig.socialLinks.map((link) => (
            <a
              aria-label={link.text}
              href={link.href}
              target="_blank"
              class="prose-link text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center p-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700"
            >
              <i class:list={[link.icon]} class="text-xl mr-2" />
              {link.text}
            </a>
          ))
        }
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg">
        Or email me at
        <a
          class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200"
          aria-label={siteConfig.email}
          href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}
        >
          {siteConfig.email}
        </a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
